data.description: Newer built, 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom craftsman-style townhouse located in the serene West Valley area. Inviting open floor plan, where the living, dining, and kitchen areas seamlessly connect. The kitchen boasts soft-close cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and convenient barn doors leading to the pantry. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms and a laundry room. The primary bedroom features a private bathroom, a walk-in closet, and an adjacent extra room, which can also serve as a second walk-in closet, office or nursery. Stay cool during hot Montana summers with Central Air. Nearby you will find the community playground and a dog park. Take a stroll through the walking paths, or explore designated open spaces—all while taking in picturesque mountain views. Convenience is key, and this prime location provides easy access to shopping, dining, and outdoor activities. Call Tim Stocklin (406) 407-7509 or your Real Estate Professional.
